WEBVTT

00:00:01.621 --> 00:00:05.746
Due settimane fa, ho cercato
la parola “nazionalista” su Twitter.

00:00:06.038 --> 00:00:07.913
I risultati erano piuttosto coloriti:

00:00:07.913 --> 00:00:11.288
espressioni come
“spavaldo coglione razzista”,

00:00:11.288 --> 00:00:12.288
(Risate)

00:00:12.288 --> 00:00:14.079
“idiota suprematista bianco”,

00:00:14.454 --> 00:00:16.371
“burattini fascisti”,

00:00:16.371 --> 00:00:17.371
(Risate)

00:00:17.371 --> 00:00:20.288
“orwelliano, hitleriano, spaventoso”.

00:00:20.288 --> 00:00:22.413
Poi ho cercato la parola “globalista”

00:00:22.413 --> 00:00:25.329
e ho ottenuto risultati
come “socialisti venduti”,

00:00:25.663 --> 00:00:28.163
“disgustosa propaganda corporativa”,

00:00:28.663 --> 00:00:31.038
“padroni finanziari elitisti”,